NAME

DateTime::Locale::jv - Locale data examples for the Javanese (jv) locale

DESCRIPTION

This pod file contains examples of the locale data available for the Javanese locale.

Date Formats

Full 

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = Selasa, 5 Februari 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = Jumat, 22 Desember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = Sabtu, 15 September -10

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Februari 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Desember 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 September -10

Medium

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Feb 2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Des 1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sep -10

Short

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05-02-2008
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22-12-1995
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15-09--10

Datetime Formats

Full

Long

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 5 Februari 2008 18:30:30 UTC
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22 Desember 1995 09:05:02 UTC
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 September -10 04:44:23 UTC

Medium

  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15 Sep -10, 04:44:23

   2008-02-05T18:30:30 = 05-02-2008, 18:30
   1995-12-22T09:05:02 = 22-12-1995, 09:05
  -0010-09-15T04:44:23 = 15-09--10, 04:44
